RUNNING PAYROLL
Viewing Past Payroll Runs

After running payroll in Mangomint, you can:

View past payroll runs

Download reports for each payroll run including the Payroll Journal and Cash Requirements reports

View and download workers’ paystubs for each payroll run

To view past payroll runs, open the Payroll app and select Options > View past payroll runs.

Select View details next to a payroll run to view the details of that run.

Once you select View details for a payroll run, you can use the "..." menu to download the Payroll Journal and Cash Requirements reports for that payroll run. If you need these reports for another date range besides the payroll period, please reach out to chat support.

To view or download a worker’s paystub, select View details next to the worker and select Print earnings statement.

Workers can also view their paystubs via their profile menu.

Can't find what you're looking for?

Start a chat with us to talk to a real person and get your questions answered, or browse our on-demand videos.
